              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3><img src="/images/icons/efficient.png" width="32"/> Pragmatic approach</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
              <strong>Tired of your ORM limitations ?</strong>
              <p>Since 4 years, Pomm sets the database at developers fingertips without the arduousness of an abstraction layer. It grants developers with unlimited access to SQL and database features while proposing a high level API over low level drivers.</p>
                <p><br /><a href="{{ app.url_generator.generate('main_about') }}">Read more&#133;</a></p>
