              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
              <strong>Be productive in a matter of seconds.</strong>
              <p>With its client oriented kernel, Pomm2 gives an easy access to powerful Postgresql features. It also comes with a CLI tool to help developers inspect database structures and generate mapping classes.<br />Using a modular distribution is the best way to comply with everyone's way of doing the things.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
